    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-build-create-business-apps-and-processes-without-code-chennai-india/ev-p/13987701</id>
    <title>🇮🇳 SAP Build: Create Business Apps and Processes Without Code(Chennai, India)</title>
    <updated>2025-01-16T08:04:29.568000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;REGISTRATION IS NOW CLOSED FOR THIS EVEN&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;T&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;-&amp;nbsp;We will send confirmation emails to first 30 registered participants in couple of weeks.&amp;nbsp;Please comment below in case you want to be considered in the waitlist. If there are any dropouts, we can consider including those in the waitlist.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam__;!!GF_29dbcQIUBPA!ywvFt4py1B3_IuUnpF-227A8WNSUvXyPt2KI03WB6h6Cb7Aq8seVA-43YXWHQncW6VnzteHJZvo3b2UpxVJHa0Xv6J3X-vx0$" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;event will give you a hands-on experience with SAP Build for building apps and business processes without code (&lt;STRONG&gt;Low Code/No Code&lt;/STRONG&gt;).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You will get to know the environment by creating:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business app for an online store (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Apps).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business process for approving purchases (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Process Automation).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A business website (&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP Build Work Zone).&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You will get to know the &lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build lobby&lt;/STRONG&gt;, where you access all your SAP Build artifacts, and get a deeper understanding of the following topics:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build Apps&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Connecting to a backend service&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Building UIs&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Binding data&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Navigation&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Triggering processes from your app&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Deploy App to BTP&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build Process Automation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Creating a process&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Adding approvals&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Creating actions&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Calling SAP backends (SAP S/4HANA Cloud and CAP services)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Updating data&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Conditions and GoTo flows&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Custom variables&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;SAP Build Work Zone(Standard Edition)&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create site&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create page&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Create space&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Embed a Build App&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/139411i4D4B2C159632ECD9/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Location&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P data-unlink="true"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Business Core Solutions&amp;nbsp;(BCS), No 162, Essar Construction, Kundrathur High Road, Gerugambakkam, Chennai 600122&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is an&lt;STRONG&gt; in-person&lt;/STRONG&gt; event&amp;nbsp;only&amp;nbsp;(not virtual)&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thank you to Business Core Solutions&amp;nbsp;(BCS)&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;for hosting&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Date&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thursday, February 6th, 2025, from &lt;STRONG&gt;9:00 to 16:00 IST&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;A light lunch will be served.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Language&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;English&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;The instructors are SAP Developer Advocates&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/156020"&gt;@Rekha_DR&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298"&gt;@eshrinivasan&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/139411i4D4B2C159632ECD9/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1208570977"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Please note that spaces are limited to&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;30&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;If you want to attend, register by clicking the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Yes&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;button in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Will you be attending?&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;section.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" style="width: 999px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/139411i4D4B2C159632ECD9/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" alt="2023-12-24_18-40-33.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H3 id="toc-hId-1012057472"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/H3&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Prerequisites&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;UL&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Bring your own laptop with power adapter and have a supported Web browser such as Google Chrome or Firefox installed on your laptop.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;LI&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Complete these SAP Build prerequisites&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;before&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;you come:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://urldefense.com/v3/__https:/developers.sap.com/tutorials/codejam-0-prerequisites.html__;!!GF_29dbcQIUBPA!ywvFt4py1B3_IuUnpF-227A8WNSUvXyPt2KI03WB6h6Cb7Aq8seVA-43YXWHQncW6VnzteHJZvo3b2UpxVJHa0Xv6Ma3QOYW$" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Set Up Prerequisites for SAP Build CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/sap-build-create-business-apps-and-processes-without-code-chennai-india/ev-p/13987701"/>
    <published>2025-01-16T08:04:29.568000+01:00</published>
