    <title>🇮🇳 Getting Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA</title>
    <updated>2025-01-29T06:05:22.738000+01:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>eshrinivasan</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/148298</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;SPAN class=""&gt;&lt;U&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;REGISTRATION IS NOW CLOSED FOR THIS EVEN&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;T&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/U&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;event is on the topic of&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Getting&amp;nbsp;Started with Machine Learning using SAP HANA&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;and Python&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;. You do not need to have any background in the topic, but a lot of curiosity!&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;You'll become acquainted with how embedded Machine Learning in SAP HANA can be used to build ML models. In working through this CodeJam you'll also become familiar with how the SAP Business Application Studio can be used to work with Jupyter notebooks.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;This is a&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;free&amp;nbsp;in-person event&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;and is planned for&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Tuesday, March 4th&amp;nbsp;in&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;Kolkata, India&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;from &lt;STRONG&gt;10:00 to 16:00 IST&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The language of the event and the content will be in English.&amp;nbsp;The instructor is&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/developer-advocates.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Developer Advocate&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Vitaliy Rudnytskiy&